text: Jeļena Ostapenko and Eva Paalma were the defending champions, but neither player chose to participate this year. Emma Laine and Eugeniya Pashkova won the title, defeating Mia Nicole Eklund and Olivia Pimiä in the final, 6–4, 6–0. == Seeds == # Emma Laine / Eugeniya Pashkova (champions) # Anastasia Bukhanko / Vanda Lukács (first round/quarterfinals) == Draw == == References == * Draw Orto-Laakarit Open - Doubles 2014 WD
